TunableTuple.description:
Two sets of species that determine if a pair of Sims can be given this relationship track. Each pair of Sims must match themselves to the opposite species lists. Example 1: species_list_one = { HUMAN } species_list_two = { DOG }
Will pass if a Human and a Dog Sim are being attempted to give this relationship track. This will not be allowed if two Humans or two Dogs are attempted to be given this track.
Example 2: species_list_one = { HUMAN } species_list_two = { HUMAN, DOG }
Will pass for a relationship between two Humans or a Dog and a Human are attempted to be given this track.
